<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A0000008" svcinfotypenbr = "01" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Warning for Wheel (with Tire) Removal
</title>
<attention1>
<ptxt>
Do not remove all wheel bolts or nuts, but leave at least one bolt or nut for each wheel to prevent the wheel from dropping. When removing the remaining bolt(s) or nut(s), hold the wheel so as not to let it fall down.
</ptxt>
</attention1>
</servinfo>
